        <p>
          <a href="https://docs.bws.ninja/marketplace-solutions/bws.nft.gamecube" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Fan Game Cube</a> enables fans to own virtual zones of real sports fields through NFTs. These digital assets connect directly to live in-game events like goals and plays, allowing fans to earn points based on real-world athletic performance.
        </p>
        <p>
          Building on this core mechanic, the platform targets sports clubs, leagues, athlete brands, and IP holders seeking innovative digital revenue streams. Rather than replacing traditional engagement, it transforms passive viewership into active participation through gamified ownership.
        </p>
        <p>
          The proof is in the adoption: new games are being scheduled with selections from over 200 global sports projects. This demonstrates how blockchain technology can create meaningful fan engagement that goes far beyond traditional sponsorship and merchandise models.
        </p>
        <figure style="float: right; margin: 0 0 1rem 1rem; min-height: 500px; max-height: 600px;">
